{"tid":1507970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我建議大家以制服黑狗為主要目標","createTime":"2019-08-26T11:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T11:29:31.000Z","uid":18238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47d928b5db3c1ed351e33d0ead2c441c8115ee14","tid":1507970,"uid":18238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"大家都知呢家瘋狗症咁嚴重，剩係打狗其實除左雙方受傷之外都冇乜太大作用<br />\n<br />\n所以以後大家見到落單狗應該立刻制服，然後以索帶將狗隻綁係隔黎欄杆或者燈柱示眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同狗隻搏鬥期間應主要攻擊下肢，盡量令對方失去平衡然<br />\n後立刻制服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，紮起左之後盡快和平散去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我唔建議大家搶狗隻既裝備（由其係槍），咁樣會被對方有位入，可能得不償失"},{"pid":"5966772cf0800c84a3a5d261fa421f12f51890e8","tid":1507970,"uid":18238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da48e081c511070aa0c336122e05c660e5c3a8e","tid":1507970,"uid":18238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e572a876d005a52dc435d346b3743ff736c7b4f","tid":1507970,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.g